---

<section
  id="specialization"
  class="section relative overflow-hidden"
  style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FAF9F6 0%, #F5F0FA 50%, #F0FBF8 100%);"
>
  <div class="container relative z-10">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col items-center text-center" data-animate-group>
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#E8F2F8] px-4 py-2 text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#A3C4D9]"
        data-animate-child
      >
        <span class="flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center">
          <i data-lucide="heart-handshake" class="h-4 w-4 text-[#A3C4D9]" stroke-width="1.6"></i>
        </span>
        Áreas de enfoque
      </div>

      <h2
        class="mt-5 text-[34px] font-bold leading-normal tracking-normal text-[#3D3D3D] md:text-[44px]"
        data-animate-child
      >
        Acompañando su crecimiento en cada etapa
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-[18px] font-normal leading-normal tracking-normal text-[#6B6B6B]" data-animate-child>
        Cuidado especializado, adaptado a las necesidades emocionales de cada etapa del desarrollo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3" data-animate-group>
      <article class="rounded-[26px] bg-white/95 p-6 shadow-soft" data-animate-child>
        <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#B8F5E8_0%,#8DE4D3_100%)] text-white">
          <i data-lucide="baby" class="h-6 w-6" stroke-width="1.7"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-5 text-[22px] font-bold leading-normal tracking-normal text-[#3D3D3D]">Terapia infantil</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15px] font-normal leading-[160%] tracking-normal text-[#6B6B6B]">
          Abordaje lúdico y creativo para niñas y niños de 4 a 11 años, fortaleciendo expresión emocional y habilidades de
          regulación.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[26px] bg-white/95 p-6 shadow-soft" data-animate-child>
        <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#D4C8E8_0%,#B8A9D4_100%)] text-white">
          <i data-lucide="users" class="h-6 w-6" stroke-width="1.7"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-5 text-[22px] font-bold leading-normal tracking-normal text-[#3D3D3D]">Terapia adolescente</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15px] font-normal leading-[160%] tracking-normal text-[#6B6B6B]">
          Acompañamiento para adolescentes en identidad, vínculos, autoestima y desafíos emocionales propios de esta etapa.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[26px] bg-white/95 p-6 shadow-soft" data-animate-child>
        <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,#B8E4F5_0%,#8AD4ED_100%)] text-white">
          <i data-lucide="graduation-cap" class="h-6 w-6" stroke-width="1.7"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-5 text-[22px] font-bold leading-normal tracking-normal text-[#3D3D3D]">Jóvenes adultos</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[15px] font-normal leading-[160%] tracking-normal text-[#6B6B6B]">
          Orientación para jóvenes en transición a la adultez: autonomía, toma de decisiones, relaciones y proyecto de vida.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center" data-animate-group>
      <p class="text-[20px] font-semibold leading-[140%] text-[#3D3D3D]" data-animate-child>Motivos de consulta frecuentes</p>
      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3" data-animate-child>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#DDF8F1] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#3E9E8B]">Ansiedad</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#E5DAF5] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#7A67B5]">Depresión</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#DCEFFC] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#5E9FCB]">Autoestima</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#FBE2DA] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#D27A62]">Conducta</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#FFF1DD] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#D19552]">Regulación emocional</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#FFF7DD] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#C39B3F]">Estrés escolar</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-[#F9E0EC] px-5 py-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-[#B66892]">Habilidades sociales</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-8 top-16 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-[#E7F7F3] opacity-20 blur-xl"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-10 top-20 h-16 w-16 rounded-[16px] bg-[#F4EAFB] opacity-22 rotate-12 blur-[2px]"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 h-36 w-36 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[#EAF4FF] opacity-18 blur-xl"></div>
</section>
